title: Dear Freud - Novel Updates
tags: Autism   Cold Love Interests   Crime   Devoted Love Interests   Female Protagonist   Handsome Male Lead   Lawyers   Modern Day   Multiple Personalities   Past Trauma
author: Jiu Yue Xi   玖月晞
description: Eight years ago, he left without saying goodbye leaving Zhen Yi wondering. A lawsuit made her a notorious lawyer. And after their parting, he became a psychologist. Case after case, she hopped onto them. In the face of the case, she always kept a calm mind and is always enthusiastic. When there is danger, he can save her, and when she is lost, he can accompany her. Along the way, overcoming numerous difficulties, the contest of high IQ was ushered in a happy ending.>
